{"tid":2384553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"張國鈞站馬路接受《點新聞》採訪 遭警喝斥「上返行人路！」","createTime":"2021-01-28T15:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T02:33:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":317,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"a2fadba7a55b02dfa21cb8b5d5ffac0b6eb35c1f","tid":2384553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/gogogogo.jpg?itok=CNItaV6K\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2Fgogogogo.jpg%3Fitok%3DCNItaV6K&h=20617a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒報導）政府再次於晚上突襲封區，7時起將北角錦屏街東發大廈A、B、C和D座劃為「受限區域」。昨晚曾到東發大廈C座派物資的民建聯立法會議員張國鈞，今日再拉隊到場視察。<br />\n<br />\n張國鈞甫到達即接受《點新聞》採訪，惟錦屏街只剩一邊行人路開放，並已佈滿記者，張需於行人路較狹窄的轉角受訪。他受訪時一度站在馬路上，不久後被警員喝斥：「上返行人路！」張即時後退至行人路上繼續受訪，警員及警方傳媒聯絡隊之後亦不時大聲提醒記者注意安全，需在行人路上採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080498&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=7a01c358\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080498&h=64063303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080498</a>"},{"pid":"808c0450f9f1f78d213c67152bb28f9fdb6b37a4","tid":2384553,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a54e9a4830c8155a567c8d4daa203cf4950f1f","tid":2384553,"uid":53498,"like":311,"dislike":1,"score":310,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"唔使扑返兩棍先"},{"pid":"b2cf12e10e18e728d27e77b13f3508a37a2f9776","tid":2384553,"uid":78892,"like":172,"dislike":3,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"請獻世派食賞花杏仁露<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eff9186c